Description: Open Data Communities offers Linked Data access to the Index of Multiple Deprivation datasets from the Department of Communities and Local Government.This provides a range of useful information covering population- income- education- health- environment and availability of key community facilities for both 2007 and 2010. Each dataset contains values for a single indicator and a single year- with one value for each of the 32484 LSOAs in England. In addition there are supporting datasets- such as the list of all LSOAs and their locations. Each dataset has a page that explains more about the data it contains and how it's organised. The English Indices of Multiple Deprivation (IMD) 2010 were released on March 24th 2011. ### Subpackages:package:odc-lsoa
